{"heading":"John the Baptist preaches in Judæa—Jesus is baptized, and the Father acclaims Him as His Beloved Son.","number":3,"verseCount":17,"verses":[[1,["In those days came ",["John the Baptist",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—H 1:72","pgp/js-h/1.72"],"."]]],", preaching in the wilderness of Judæa,"]],[2,["And saying, ",["Repent",["study-note-ref","a",["The Greek word denotes “a change of heart or mind,” i.e., “a conversion.” ",["Alma 7:9","bofm/alma/7.9"],"; ",["9:25 (25–26)","bofm/alma/9.25"],"; ",["Hel. 5:32","bofm/hel/5.32"],"; ",["D&C 33:10","dc-testament/dc/33.10"],"."]]]," ye: for the ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 10:9","nt/luke/10.9"],". ",["TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven","tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"],"; ",["Kingdom of God, on Earth","tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"],"."]]]," of heaven ",["is at hand",["study-note-ref","c",["GR has come. ",["Isa. 56:1","ot/isa/56.1"],"; ",["Matt. 4:17","nt/matt/4.17"],"; ",["D&C 39:19","dc-testament/dc/39.19"],"."]]],"."]],[3,["For this is he that was spoken of by the prophet ",["Esaias",["study-note-ref","a",["See ",["JST Luke 3:4–11 (Appendix)","jst/jst-luke/3.4-11"],". ",["TG Foreordination","tg/foreordination"],"."]]],", saying, The ",["voice",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 40:3","ot/isa/40.3"],"; ",["Mark 1:3","nt/mark/1.3"],"; ",["Luke 3:4","nt/luke/3.4"],"; ",["John 1:23","nt/john/1.23"],"; ",["D&C 65:3","dc-testament/dc/65.3"],"; ",["88:66","dc-testament/dc/88.66"],"."]]]," of one crying in the ",["",1190],"wilderness, ",["Prepare",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Ne. 10:8 (7–10)","bofm/1-ne/10.8"],"; ",["D&C 34:6","dc-testament/dc/34.6"],"; ",["65:1 (1–2)","dc-testament/dc/65.1"],"; ",["84:26","dc-testament/dc/84.26"],"."]]]," ye the way of the Lord, make his ",["paths",["study-note-ref","d",[["Alma 7:19 (9, 19)","bofm/alma/7.19"],"."]]]," straight."]],[4,["And the same John had his ",["raiment",["study-note-ref","a",["GR garment. See also ",["2 Kgs. 1:8","ot/2-kgs/1.8"],"."]]]," of ",["camel’s",["study-note-ref","b",[["Zech. 13:4","ot/zech/13.4"],"."]]]," hair, and a leathern girdle about his loins; and his meat was ",["locusts",["study-note-ref","c",[["Lev. 11:22","ot/lev/11.22"],"."]]]," and wild honey."]],[5,["Then went out to him Jerusalem, and all Judæa, and all the region round about Jordan,"]],[6,["And were baptized of him in Jordan, ",["confessing",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Confession","tg/confession"],"."]]]," their sins."]],[7,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"But when he saw many of the Pharisees and Sadducees come to his ",["baptism",["study-note-ref","a",["See ",["JST Matt. 9:18–21 (Appendix)","jst/jst-matt/9.18-21"],". ",["Luke 7:29 (29–30)","nt/luke/7.29"],"."]]],", he said unto them, O ",["generation of vipers",["study-note-ref","b",["GR crop of serpents. ",["Matt. 12:34","nt/matt/12.34"],"; ",["23:33","nt/matt/23.33"],"; ",["Alma 9:8","bofm/alma/9.8"],"; ",["10:17 (17–25)","bofm/alma/10.17"],"."]]],", who hath ",["warned",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Warn","tg/warn"],"."]]]," you to flee from the wrath to come?"]],[8,[["Bring",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST Matt. 3:34–36 (Appendix)","jst/jst-matt/3.34-36"],"."]]]," forth therefore fruits ",["meet for",["study-note-ref","b",["GR appropriate to, worthy of."]]]," ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Baptism, Qualifications for","tg/baptism-qualifications-for"],"; ",["Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]],":"]],[9,["And think not to say within yourselves, We have Abraham ",["to our father",["study-note-ref","a",["GR as our father."]]],": for I say unto you, that God is able of these stones to raise up children unto Abraham."]],[10,["And now also the axe is laid unto the root of the trees: therefore every tree which ",["bringeth",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 5:36 (36–41)","bofm/alma/5.36"],"; ",["3 Ne. 14:19","bofm/3-ne/14.19"],"; ",["D&C 52:18","dc-testament/dc/52.18"],"; ",["97:7","dc-testament/dc/97.7"],"."]]]," not forth good fruit is ",["hewn",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 13:7","nt/luke/13.7"],"; ",["Jacob 5:42 (42–66)","bofm/jacob/5.42"],"."]]]," down, and cast into the fire."]],[11,[["I",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST Matt. 3:38–40 (Appendix)","jst/jst-matt/3.38-40"],"."]]]," indeed ",["baptize",["study-note-ref","b",[["Acts 19:3 (1–7)","nt/acts/19.3"],"; ",["2 Ne. 31:5 (5–10)","bofm/2-ne/31.5"],"."]]]," you with water unto ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Baptism, Qualifications for","tg/baptism-qualifications-for"],"."]]],": but ",["he",["study-note-ref","d",["See ",["JST John 1:27–34 (Appendix)","jst/jst-john/1.27-34"],"."]]]," that cometh after me is mightier than I, whose shoes I am not ",["worthy",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Worthiness","tg/worthiness"],"."]]]," to bear: he shall ",["baptize",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Holy Ghost, Baptism of","tg/holy-ghost-baptism-of"],"."]]]," you with the Holy Ghost, and ",["with",["clarity-word"]]," ",["fire",["study-note-ref","g",[["D&C 19:31","dc-testament/dc/19.31"],"."]]],":"]],[12,["Whose ",["fan",["study-note-ref","a",[["Jer. 51:2","ot/jer/51.2"],"."]]]," ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," in his hand, and he will throughly purge his floor, and gather his wheat into the ",["garner",["study-note-ref","b",["GR storehouse."]]],"; but he will burn up the chaff with unquenchable ",["fire",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 43:32","dc-testament/dc/43.32"],"; ",["63:34 (33–34)","dc-testament/dc/63.34"],"; ",["101:66","dc-testament/dc/101.66"],"."]]],"."]],[13,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"Then cometh Jesus from Galilee to Jordan unto John, to be ",["baptized",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Baptism of","tg/jesus-christ-baptism-of"],"."]]]," of him."]],[14,["But John forbad him, saying, I have need to be baptized of thee, and comest thou to me?"]],[15,[["And",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST Matt. 3:43–46 (Appendix)","jst/jst-matt/3.43-46"],"."]]]," Jesus answering said unto him, ",["Suffer",["study-note-ref","b",["GR Permit it now."]]]," ",["it to be so",["clarity-word"]]," now: for thus it ",["becometh us",["study-note-ref","c",["GR is fitting for us."]]]," to ",["fulfil",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Baptism, Essential","tg/baptism-essential"],"."]]]," all ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"; ",["Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],". Then he suffered him."]],[16,["And Jesus, when he was ",["baptized",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Baptism","tg/baptism"],"; ",["Baptism, Immersion","tg/baptism-immersion"],"."]]],", went up ",["straightway",["study-note-ref","b",["GR immediately."]]]," out of the water: and, lo, the heavens were opened unto him, and he saw the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG God, Spirit of","tg/god-spirit-of"],"."]]]," of God descending like a ",["dove",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Holy Ghost, Dove, Sign of","tg/holy-ghost-dove-sign-of"],"."]]],", and lighting upon him:"]],[17,["And lo a ",["voice",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mark 9:7","nt/mark/9.7"],"; ",["Luke 9:35 (34–36)","nt/luke/9.35"],". ",["TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature","tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"],"; ",["God, Manifestations of","tg/god-manifestations-of"],"."]]]," from heaven, saying, This is my ",["beloved",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 17:5","nt/matt/17.5"],"; ",["3 Ne. 11:7","bofm/3-ne/11.7"],"; ",["JS—H 1:17","pgp/js-h/1.17"],". ",["TG Witness of the Father","tg/witness-of-the-father"],"."]]]," ",["Son",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Godhead","tg/godhead"],"; ",["God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship","tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"],"."]]],", in whom I am well pleased."]]],"volume":"nt"}